    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make providing job references for employees compulsory ",
        "additional_details": "Help give adults the best opportunity to improve their lives.",
        "background": "The UK government should make it compulsory for employers to provide references for staff after 1 year of service. References are not compulsory and some skilled workers are being forced to claim benefits. ",
